Write a user-defined function which wraps the stringr function str_replace_na(), and use it to replace any NA values in the vendor_name column with the string ‚ÄúNo vendor‚Äù instead. (Test it on the data from 2019 so you‚Äôre not pulling everything into memory)




# Preview the distinct vendor names before we start
nyc_taxi |&gt;
