ProblemSolution 1



How many taxi pickups were recorded in 2019 from the three major airports covered by the NYC Taxis data set (JFK, LaGuardia, Newark)? (Hint: you can use stringr::str_detect() to help you find pickup zones with the word ‚ÄúAirport‚Äù in them)




pickup_location &lt;- read_csv_arrow(here::here("data/taxi_zone_lookup.csv"))

pickup_location &lt;- pickup_location |&gt;
  select(
    pickup_location_id = LocationID,
    borough = Borough,
    pickup_zone = Zone
  ) 


pickup_location_arrow &lt;- arrow_table(
  pickup_location, 
  schema = schema(
    pickup_location_id = int64(),
    borough = utf8(),
    pickup_zone = utf8()
  ))

nyc_taxi |&gt;
  filter(year == 2019) |&gt;
  left_join(pickup_location_arrow) |&gt;
  filter(str_detect(pickup_zone, "Airport")) |&gt;
  count(pickup_zone) |&gt;
  collect()

